>    V8 =3D Vargr?  (what flavor?)   (lishun)
Vargr. Council of the Four-Pair

>    Vv =3D Vargr?  (what flavor?)   (lishun)
Vargr. Voekhaeb Society

>    Vx =3D Vargr?  (what flavor?)   (lishun)
Vargr. Antares Pact

>    V7 =3D Vargr?  (what flavor?)   (vland)
