    'body' => '> From: tiger@datasync.com (Paul Walker)
> Subject: TNE Bashers
>
> >Date: Thu, 2 May 1996 12:03:04 -0400 (EDT)
> >From: "Joseph M. Saul" <jmsaul@us.itd.umich.edu>
