Traveller leave open many many adventure options.  Slow communication
speeds means that characters who are (falsely I am sure!) accused of some
crime can keep one step ahead of the law.  Slow travel times makes
outthinkng your opponent all the more important in large naval campaigs.

Like I said, a choice had to be made, and the choices that went into
Traveller have alot to do with the amazing diversity of game play that can
be had from it.


