    'body' => '=> 	-Biology	: Includes Xenobiology as a matter of course at 

I still believe that these two skills should be separated, since Biology usually
deals with the workings of familiar biological organisms native to the planet
where the skill was learned.  Xenobiology, on the other hand, is much more
theoretical and deals with "things foreign"

=> 	-Geology	: 
=> [this is literally "knowledge of Earth", can anyone suggest a more 
