Actually, geology deals with the study of a planet\'s crust.  Things such as
weather patterns would fall under "meteorology".  If you wanted to lump all of
them together, how \'bout "Planetary Science"?

=> Interrogation (D)

I wouldn\'t consider this a default skill.  Although anyone can threaten someone
with physical violence to gain information, the actual *skill* should be used to
determine if information given under such a threat  is truthful or not.

=> Intimidation (D)

This should not be confused with "Torture" since the proper application of pain
(for whatever purpose) also requires the intimidator to know when to stop before
any permanent harm is done (such as death  8-)

