	[Players can also make up their own member of this group.]


***OTHER SKILLS**************************

Athletics (G)
	Running		
	Swimming
	Climbing/Moutaineering
	Sport (G)(Choose one).

Carousing (RPG)	
Jack-of-all-Trades
