(other than a generic one) and see if the setting can be completely
distinguished from the rules.

As for TSR and their many campaign worlds.  Greyhawk was their
official and only campaign world until 1986 when it (along with Gary
Gygax) was dropped.  At that point they created the Forgotten Realms.
